@model PagedList.IPagedList<_0306191062_vohoangphuc.Areas.Admin.Models.TaiKhoan>
@using PagedList.Mvc;
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Danh Sách Tài Khoản";
    Layout = "~/Areas/Admin/Views/Shared/_Layout.cshtml";
}
<div class="col-lg-12 grid-margin stretch-card">
    <div class="card">
        <div class="card-body">
            <h4 class="card-title">Danh sách tài khoản</h4>
            @*<form asp-action="Index" method="get">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-md-3">
                            <input type="text" name="keyword" value="@ViewBag.Keyword" class="form-control" />
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-3">
                            <select name="LoaiSanPhamId" asp-items="@ViewBag.LoaiSanPham">
                                <option>--Chọn dòng xe--</option>
                            </select>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </form>*@

            <p class="card-description">
                <a class="btn btn-danger btn-rounded btn-fw" asp-action="Create">Thêm Tài Khoản</a>
            </p>
            <div class="table-responsive">
                <table class="table table-striped">
                    <thead>
                        <tr>
                            <th>
                                Hình ảnh
                            </th>
                            <th>
                                Tên đăng nhập
                            </th>
                            <th>
                                Họ và tên
                            </th>
                            @*<th>
                                    @Html.DisplayNameFor(model => model.MatKhau)
                                </th>*@
                            <th>
                                Email
                            </th>
                            <th>
                                Số điện thoại
                            </th>
                            <th>
                                Địa chỉ
                            </th>
                            <th>
                                Chức vụ
                            </th>
                            @*<th>
                                    @Html.DisplayNameFor(model => model.TrangThai)
                                </th>*@
                            <th></th>
                        </tr>
                    </thead>
                    <tbody>
                        @foreach (var item in Model)
                        {
                            <tr>
                                <td class="py-1">
                                    <img src="~/admin/assets/images/users/@item.HinhAnh" alt="image" />
                                </td>
                                <td>
                                    @Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => item.TenNguoiDung)
                                </td>
                                <td>
                                    @Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => item.HoVaTen)
                                </td>
                                @*<td>
                                        @Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => item.MatKhau)
                                    </td>*@
                                <td>
                                    @Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => item.Email)
                                </td>
                                <td>
                                    @Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => item.SDT)
                                </td>
                                <td>
                                    @Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => item.DiaChi)
                                </td>
                                <td>
                                    @*@Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => (item.TrangThai == 1)?"Đã duyệt":"Chưa duyệt")*@
                                    @if (item.IsAdmin == true)
                                    {
                                        <b class="btn btn-success btn-rounded" style="width:90;">Admin</b>
                                    }
                                    else
                                    {
                                        <b class="btn btn-danger btn-rounded" style="width:90;">User</b>
                                    }
                                </td>

                                @*<td>
                                        @Html.DisplayFor(modelItem => item.TrangThai)
                                    </td>*@
                                <td>
                                    @*<a class="btn btn-success btn-rounded" style="width:90;" asp-action="Edit" asp-route-id="@item.Id">Edit</a>*@
                                    <a class="btn btn-info btn-rounded" style="width:90;" asp-action="Details" asp-route-id="@item.Id">Details</a>
                                    <a class="btn btn-danger btn-rounded" style="width:90;" asp-action="Delete" asp-route-id="@item.Id">Delete</a>
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                        }
                    </tbody>
                </table>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
@*Start: Phân trang*@
<nav aria-label="Page navigation example">
    <ul class="pagination">
        @*<li class="page-item disabled">
              <a class="page-link" href="#" tabindex="-1">Previous</a>
            </li>*@
        @for (int i = 0; i < Model.PageCount; i++)
        {
            <li class="page-item @(Model.PageNumber == i + 1?"active":"")">
                <a class="page-link" asp-action="Index" asp-route-page="@(i+1)">@(i+1) <span class="sr-only">(current)</span></a>
            </li>

        }

        @*<li class="page-item">
              <a class="page-link" href="#">Next</a>
            </li>*@
    </ul>
</nav>
@*End: Phân trang*@